Rainbow Jello Shots

$15

Description

Colorful and fun jello shots that are perfect for parties!

Ingredients

  • gelatin: 3 packets
  • water: 3 cups
  • sugar: 1 cup
  • flavored drink mix (various colors): 5 packets
  • vodka: 2 cups
